## Key Conventions

- Use `@/*` or configured path alias for imports. Avoid deep relative paths.
- Organize components by what they ARE (ui/, cards/, modal/, pages/, sections/), not what page they appear on.
{{#IF_SHADCN}}
- `src/components/ui/` is READ-ONLY — never modify UI library primitives. Create wrappers instead.
{{/IF_SHADCN}}
{{#IF_ZOD}}
- All Zod schemas go in a dedicated validation directory. Never define validation inline.
{{/IF_ZOD}}
{{#IF_NICE_MODAL}}
- Use `@ebay/nice-modal-react` with centralized `ModalConstant` for IDs. Register modals in barrel file.
{{/IF_NICE_MODAL}}
{{#IF_NEXTJS}}
- Each major section should be a page route. Layouts provide persistent shells. Use `usePathname()` + `<Link>` for navigation.
{{/IF_NEXTJS}}

